title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 5 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 5 2022
description:
Oklahoma Governor Kevin Stitt joins Clay and Buck, discusses signing bill to halt gender transition services at OU Children’s Hospital, the border and gas prices. Callers who moved to Florida from blue states. Plus, C&B reminisce about how many times they have each moved. Herschel Walker in dead heat with Warnock, Dems try to take him out with an October Surprise. Despicable Democrats who elected Ted Kennedy and Bill Clinton try to pull a Kavanaugh on Herschel Walker. Whoopi Goldberg: GOP nominated Herschel Walker only because he's black. C&B end the hour with fired-up callers.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
